summary: This document appears to be an FBI Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) report detailing the creation of a master copy of video images extracted from hard drives as part of an investigation. It is marked as 'FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY - ENFORCEMENT SENSITIVE' and relates to case number 90A-NY-3151227.

events.title: CART Master Copy Creation
events.description: The FBI Computer Analysis Response Team created a master copy of video images taken from hard drives as part of investigation 90A-NY-3151227.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) report related to case 90A-NY-3151227.
A master copy of video images extracted from hard drives was created as of June 21, 2021.
The document is marked 'FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY - ENFORCEMENT SENSITIVE', indicating its sensitive law enforcement nature.
The report references 'MCC NY', which likely stands for Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York.
The document is part of the Epstein case files, suggesting the video analysis is connected to the investigation of Jeffrey Epstein.
